abstract: College Basketball Roundup; University of Kansas beats Chaminade University, 123-72, in round one of Maui Invitational; other men's and women's scores noted.
lead_paragraph: The No. 19 Commodores put together a 27-4 run to open the game and never looked back against the Red Storm during the first round of the Maui Invitational.

headline.main: Kansas Thrashes Chaminade in Its Maui Invitational Opener
headline.print_headline: Kansas Routs Chaminade to Advance at Maui Invitational
